{{outlet}}

<div class="banner" style="background-image: url(./img/fist.jpg);">
  <div class="mask"></div>
  <h1 class="banner-header">Are your representatives representing <i>you?</i></h1>
  <p class="banner-content">
    Democracy begins at the local level. Now, there's no excuse not to know who's representing you
    and making decisions on your behalf. Poligap bridges the gap between regular people like you
    and local government--providing the tools and information necessary to influence the policies
    and elections that directly impact you and the place you live.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="text-wrapper white-background-content right-align">
  <div class="twin">
    <h3>Change begins with knowing who's calling the shots</h3>
    <p>
      Dig into the lives of your local representatives, or those from around the country. See how they're all connected
      and where each rep stands on the issues that are most important to you and your community.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="twin image-wrapper">
    <img class="image-full network-icon" src="./img/connections.svg">
  </div>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>
<div class="gray-background-content triplets">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="triplet center">
      <img class="front-page-callout-image matched-images" src="./img/senator.svg">
      <h3>82%</h3>
      <p>
        Of people can't name their state senators.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="triplet center">
      <img class="front-page-callout-image matched-images" src="./img/ballot.svg">
      <h3>76%</h3>
      <p>
        Of people don't know what's on their ballot.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="triplet center">
      <img class="front-page-callout-image matched-images" src="./img/vote.svg">
      <h3>68%</h3>
      <p>
        Of people didn't vote in the last election.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container center white-background-content">
  <h2>
    These numbers are pretty bad, huh?<br>
    Let's do something about it.
  </h2>

  <div class="blue-button">
    <p>
      Show me my reps
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
